You are helping to create synthetic training data for fine-tuning a small language model that audits user support chat transcripts related to various infrastructure issues. The goal is to generate realistic chat conversations, for these different issues, between users and helpdesk agents, along with correct audit labels for the given audit parameters.
The various infrastructure issues in scope are - Unable to login to application, Device not active, Email not updating, Upgrade link not working, Unable to login to PC, Multifactor authentication not working, Account locked out and Session hanging.
The audit labels in scope are compliance check, resolution status, agent tone and customer sentiment. The possible values for the various audit labels are: compliance check - Yes / No / Partial; resolution status - Resolved / Escalated / Unresolved; agent tone - Polite / Neutral / Rude; customer sentiment - Positive / Neutral / Negative.
